snippet.title: Must-Play Quake - Marcher Fortress
snippet.description:
Welcome to a new series of videos called Must-Play Quake. The game is over 20 years old and there are some forgotten maps and mods that have been overshadowed by more recent releases. There’s plenty more Quake content you may have missed and that’s what this series is all about.

Download The Marcher Fortress Mod / Map here: https://www.quaddicted.com/reviews/kinn_marcher.html

Bastion of the Underworld
https://www.quaddicted.com/reviews/kinn_bastion.html

Insomnia (CZG07)
https://www.quaddicted.com/reviews/czg07.html

Shalrath replacement model by Chillo
https://twitter.com/DanielWienerson/status/979872550296563713
https://t.co/FoQFcBjsZg

Companion Interview with Kinn on func_msgbaord
http://www.celephais.net/board/view_thread.php?id=28271&start=197
